{
  "stem": "26609.12",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Chief of Gestapo wrote down something, he left, and I was a good Christian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Next day, the men with a long paper, a roll of paper, and read something, Wanda Gru-- opened the door, Wanda Grabowienska, you're free.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't go straight away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's was stupid, what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a little picture of the Maria, the Holy Maria on the wall, which we're not-- we were not allowed to put it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when no one saw it, the Germans, we put it on there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was not allowed to believe, even, the Polish and Polish-- in a religion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I fell on my knees and I wanted to thank her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Before I tell you about the songs that I learned there, they told me, Wanda, go quick, otherwise, if you don't go, they won't take you-- let you go anymore.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I got up, I went out, and went down the stairs, went out free.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was not the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That priest helped me-- he helped himself and helped me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As I went out, I felt very sensitive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I felt that someone was behind me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I turned my head and there were two men from the police sent after me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They still didn't believe me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They still sent after me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Instead to go home to see my child, I didn't go, because I felt them, and I had one look and I-- I noticed a secret police, [NON-ENGLISH], and I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We passed the street, because that was the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Had to go on foot, and I walked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I walked down, and they were always behind me, and I knew why.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I understood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't go-- I passed the house where-- not there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
